{dropDownValues?.pfList.map((option) => ( {option.pf_name} ))}
{dropDownValues?.servicetaxList.map((option) => ( {option.servicetax_name} ))}
{dropDownValues?.exciseDutyList.map((option) => ( {option.exciseduty_name} ))}
